{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","abstract":[],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}]}}}